reviewText: Bought this because I am a fan of  Alicia Minshew.  I thought the acting was poor and I didn't like how it was broken up into 8 minute segments.  It made watching it very unpleasant.  I dropped mine off at the local library, it was a total waste of $25.00.
its good when is S2 comming out
I liked the idea and the characters, but the segments were too brief and the interruptions were extremely annoying.
